I did this last night. Got a tell to come to a PoV group but it disbanded because of arguments even before I got invited. Only me and a 60 war from my guild were left of it. I ran to zone, gave a /tell to a guildcleric who had just logged in, &quot;/ all lfg sham&quot; gave me a 62 shammie who was lfg in the bazaar after that it was just random targetting and inviting damage dealers near me.<br>
<br>
CC gave all cave spots camped so we went to desert. Both castle walls camped so we simply sat at stairs and moved to left wall when that group left.<br>
<br>
