<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Option 1 affects all three balance areas: caster vs caster, melee vs caster, and caster vs environment. Option 2 only affects <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">caster vs melee, which with the focus items is in tolerable shape now.</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--> <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->Here is a wizard, actually one of the most notorious wizard balance advocates in the history of Everquest, admitting(although perhaps a bit grudgingly) that wizards are mostly balanced versus melees for the moment.  Compare that to the thread above, which points to wizards being weak when compared to all the other int casters...<br>
<br>
